# ADR-0001: Architecture Baseline for {{projectName}}

- **Status:** Proposed
- **Date:** {{createdDate}}
- **Context:** Need a lightweight, reproducible way to scaffold planning docs for new projects.
- **Decision:** Use Next.js (App Router) on Vercel; Handlebars templates; JSZip packaging; optional GitHub repo bootstrap via Octokit.
- **Consequences:**
  - ✅ Fast, serverless-friendly generation.
  - ✅ Easy template customization.
  - ⚠️ Large binary deps (Chromium for PDF) must stay in Serverless Fn (not Edge).
  - ⚠️ Output quality depends on user-provided metadata.

> Update future ADRs if stack changes (DB, auth, etc.).
